    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a pure analog connection to the road. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS unit overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension geometry is tight, benefiting from recently refreshed control arm bushings and Bilstein monotube dampers. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all cylinders remain excellent, offering a visceral driving experience for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
