      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response and retains its factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline capability. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, transferring power through a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the double-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has undergone professional reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension utilizes OEM-spec damping and refreshed bushings, preserving the model's signature lateral grip and communicative steering rack. While the finish shows minor aerodynamic pitting and light interior wear consistent with its age, the powertrain remains in excellent health with no signs of rod bearing fatigue or fluid leaks.",
